OL,3,GNorth West
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FHeavy
OL,6,Fshowers will clear eastwards during
OL,7,Fthe evening. Mostly dry overnight,
OL,8,Fwith clear spells at times. However, a
OL,9,Ffew light showers remain possible,
OL,10,Fmostly on higher ground. Staying
OL,11,Fbreezy along coasts by dawn. Mild for
OL,12,Fmost.
OL,13,
OL,14,CSunday:FShowers to start in the north,
OL,15,Fbut turning drier. An increasing risk
OL,16,Fof showery outbreaks of rain
OL,17,Fdeveloping as the day progresses,
OL,18,Fturning heavy over the hills later.
OL,19,FRather windy.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
